    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#oliverioDAI1"/>, p. 96, n. <citedRange>30</citedRange></bibl>, whence
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>9.31</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>013300</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/>, pp. <citedRange>171-174</citedRange> (content), p. <citedRange>311</citedRange>, number 53 (text)</bibl>.</p>
                    <p>For a general bibliography on the accounts of the damiergoi see <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr011400</ref>.
                </p>
